{"title":"将军当兵片断","authors":["里沙"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":10,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军当兵片断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里沙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂上列兵军衔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他对着镜子笑了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少年的烽火，礼花，战友……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霎时全在眼前跳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱人给他鱼肝油，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他摇头接过来，给了儿子小毛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只带走党的嘱托，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤胆红心，军装、战刀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呀，大雨云烟漫天飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开汽车送送吧？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿！他背起背包走了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂首阔步地走了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前，今朝皆一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路歌声高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看哪，劈雷和暴雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为他闪开了道！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"休息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熄灯号吹落了军营的灯火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的老兵睡啦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！月光透过树叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在他身上绣起花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，肘上补钉像一片蜡梅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"床前的鞋也快要“报销”啦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老兵呵，你经过多少冲杀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚过多少雷雨，风沙？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他翻身时，还闪出一丝微笑哩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫非在梦里看见手榴弹开花？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是和小胖子一同伏在烈日下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并肩举枪，又三中红靶？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风呵，翻山飞去吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要吹拂他花白的鬓发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晨，不等启明星升起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他又要去唤起黎明的朝霞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"球赛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵火热的掌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催得乒乓球飞起来了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锦标赛：老兵对新兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扯得观众的心鼓点般急跳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新兵猛抽球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像发火箭炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老兵把球轻轻挑回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微微一笑……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老兵喊：“加油，小伙子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我可是不好攻的碉堡”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新兵双眼紧追球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗湿了军帽也不知道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志们看呆了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里直念叨："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“最高的奖赏还能归谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肯定是老兵夺得锦标！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗬，球赛结果真妙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老兵输了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下多少激情让人们去想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个秘密老兵心里知道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你打得真好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是不能骄傲。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老兵紧握新兵手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新兵脸红了，不肯接锦标。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我媳妇要和我挑战！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说怎么办？……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说着，新兵向老兵挤眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“为我保密，不要宣传！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老兵也向新兵挤眼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不相信吗？那就别谈！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“别逗啦，老列兵！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"憨笑呵！爬上新兵的脸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱俩同举一杆枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同卧一张毯。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心事你也能看见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不找你谈找谁谈？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我思想背包袱了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和你谈了，包袱就丢完；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"‘碉堡’攻不下了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和你谈了，困难就向我低头打颤。……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“好，小伙子别谈了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑战就应战呗！……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老兵眼里闪着淳厚的光辉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用手拍着新兵宽厚的肩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“对！你给我想想条件”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新兵哈哈大笑了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我的心事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不找你谈找谁谈……”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}